1002
01:14:19,644 --> 01:14:21,501
<i>¡Tengo que correr!</i>

1003
01:14:23,076 --> 01:14:24,214
<i>¡Tengo que correr!</i>

1004
01:14:27,101 --> 01:14:29,876
<i>Yo, yo, yo, yo, yo, yo, yo tengo</i>

1005
